WEBVTT

00:02.268 --> 00:03.701
<i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries:

00:03.870 --> 00:05.895
- You must be Elena.
- How do we look alike?

00:06.072 --> 00:08.768
You're a Petrova doppelganger.
Key to breaking the curse.

00:08.942 --> 00:10.842
- Sun and the moon curse?
- Klaus is real.

00:11.011 --> 00:12.273
First generation vampire.

00:12.445 --> 00:15.141
The oldest vampire in the history
of time is after me?

00:15.315 --> 00:17.078
Elijah. He's one of the Originals.

00:17.250 --> 00:18.740
I'm prepared to offer a deal.

00:18.918 --> 00:22.081
- What kind of a deal?
- We'll draw Klaus out, I'll make certain...

00:22.255 --> 00:24.018
...your friends are unharmed.
- Then?

00:24.190 --> 00:25.885
- I kill him.
- I come bearing gifts.

00:26.159 --> 00:28.457
This is how you kill an Original.

00:28.628 --> 00:31.927
Killing Elijah would be a
suicide mission. You can't do it.

00:32.131 --> 00:33.793
Even with the dagger and white ash?

00:34.000 --> 00:37.265
If you kill Elijah,
then I'm stuck in here forever.

00:39.839 --> 00:42.307
As long as we keep
the dagger there, he stays dead.

00:42.509 --> 00:44.602
- Pretty much.
- How did you get out?

00:44.778 --> 00:48.646
I knew that if I begged you not to kill
Elijah that's exactly what you'd do.

00:48.815 --> 00:51.511
As soon as Originals die,
compulsion wears off.

00:51.684 --> 00:53.675
What did Luka tell you?

00:53.853 --> 00:56.720
He told me about your daughter.
I know Klaus has her.

00:56.956 --> 00:59.288
I want to help you get her back.
Please.

01:00.427 --> 01:01.894
No.

01:02.062 --> 01:03.620
He took my powers.

01:09.436 --> 01:11.666
Stefan, we're late for school.

01:11.838 --> 01:13.897
- Let's be later.
- Stefan, it's school.

01:14.074 --> 01:15.735
That thing we're forgetting about?

01:15.942 --> 01:17.569
- Hey.
- School?

01:17.744 --> 01:18.733
Heh, mm-mm.

01:19.746 --> 01:23.011
- Doesn't ring a bell.
- Stefan.

01:23.216 --> 01:24.581
Stefan. Okay, five minutes.

01:24.751 --> 01:27.481
- Only five minutes.
- Five minutes?

01:34.694 --> 01:36.491
Good morning, Damon.

01:40.366 --> 01:41.560
What are you doing here?

01:41.734 --> 01:43.725
- What is your problem?
- Wear her clothes?

01:43.903 --> 01:45.894
Like that's going to work.

01:46.072 --> 01:47.869
You think I'm Katherine?

01:48.041 --> 01:50.566
Why would you think that?
Katherine's in a tomb.

01:52.112 --> 01:53.875
Isn't she?

01:57.684 --> 01:59.584
What the hell's going on here?

02:00.386 --> 02:04.083
I don't know, you tell me.
Is Katherine in the tomb or not?

02:09.628 --> 02:11.722
- What are you doing?
- How could you do this?

02:11.898 --> 02:14.196
- Stefan, you're hurting me. Aah!
- Stop it, Katherine.

02:14.367 --> 02:16.232
Stop what?

02:19.906 --> 02:22.602
It's getting really easy being you.

02:24.000 --> 02:30.074
